name: Cows Are Great
description: Hi I am 11 years old and I have always loved cows.  When I first heard about NFT's I knew the first thing I had to do was create some awesome cows.  This is the very first cow I ever tried to make.  I want to give him to you all as a hello!  Our art mentor does not allow us to use our real names for safety reasons, so please call me 'IWannaBeACow'
